<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="ZenTrack — Build powerful daily habits and track your growth with a beautiful, minimal habit tracker.">
  <title>ZenTrack | Build Habits. Track Growth. Live Better.</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --primary: #6366f1;
      --primary-dark: #4f46e5;
      --accent: #10b981;
      --bg: #030712;
      --bg2: #0f172a;
      --text: #f1f5f9;
      --text-dim: #94a3b8;
      --glass: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      --glass-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      --glow: rgba(99,102,241,0.35);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ============ BACKGROUND ============ */
    .bg-orbs {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .orb {
      position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(120px); opacity: 0.2;
    }
    .orb-1 { width: 600px; height: 600px; background: var(--primary); top: -200px; left: -150px; animation: float1 10s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .orb-2 { width: 500px; height: 500px; background: var(--accent); bottom: -100px; right: -100px; animation: float2 13s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .orb-3 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: #8b5cf6; top: 40%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%,-50%); animation: float1 9s ease-in-out infinite reverse; }

    @keyframes float1 { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(-40px)} }
    @keyframes float2 { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(30px)} }

    /* ============ NAVBAR ============ */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      padding: 20px 6%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      background: rgba(3,7,18,0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    }
    .nav-brand { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-brand span { color: var(--primary); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: center; }
    .btn-login {
      padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 50px; border: 2px solid var(--glass-border);
      background: var(--glass); color: var(--text); font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-login:hover { border-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary); background: rgba(99,102,241,0.1); }
    .btn-signup {
      padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 50px; border: none;
      background: var(--primary); color: white; font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--glow);
    }
    .btn-signup:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--glow); }

    /* ============ HERO ============ */
    .hero {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      text-align: center; padding: 120px 6% 80px;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 50px;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.3);
      color: #a5b4fc; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 32px; animation: fadeDown 0.6s ease both;
    }
    .hero-badge .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:0.5;transform:scale(1.3)} }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
      font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      animation: fadeDown 0.7s 0.1s ease both;
    }
    .hero h1 .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #a78bfa, var(--accent));
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem); color: var(--text-dim);
      max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 48px;
      animation: fadeDown 0.8s 0.2s ease both;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;
      animation: fadeDown 0.9s 0.3s ease both;
    }
    .cta-primary {
      padding: 16px 40px; border-radius: 50px; border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #8b5cf6);
      color: white; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--glow);
      transition: all 0.3s; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    }
    .cta-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px var(--glow); }
    .cta-secondary {
      padding: 16px 40px; border-radius: 50px;
      border: 2px solid var(--glass-border);
      background: var(--glass); color: var(--text);
      font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    }
    .cta-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-3px); }

    @keyframes fadeDown { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-20px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }

    /* ============ STATS ============ */
    .stats-row {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 40px 6%; margin-top: -20px;
      animation: fadeDown 1s 0.4s ease both;
    }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat-num { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 4px; }

    /* ============ FEATURES ============ */
    .section {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      padding: 80px 6%; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .section-label {
      text-align: center; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--primary); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-title {
      text-align: center; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 60px; line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--glass); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      border-radius: 24px; padding: 36px 32px;
      transition: all 0.3s; cursor: default;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .feature-card::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: 24px;
      opacity: 0; transition: 0.3s;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(99,102,241,0.1), transparent 70%);
    }
    .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.4); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
    .feature-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.2);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--primary);
    }
    .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .feature-card p { color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.65; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    /* ============ HOW IT WORKS ============ */
    .steps-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 32px; position: relative;
    }
    .step {
      text-align: center; padding: 32px 24px;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #8b5cf6);
      color: white; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px var(--glow);
    }
    .step h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .step p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ============ CTA BANNER ============ */
    .cta-banner {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      margin: 40px 6% 80px;
      border-radius: 28px; padding: 64px 48px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99,102,241,0.2), rgba(139,92,246,0.15));
      border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.25);
      text-align: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-banner::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50%; left: -50%;
      width: 200%; height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99,102,241,0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cta-banner h2 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-banner p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

    /* ============ FOOTER ============ */
    footer {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
      padding: 32px 6%;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    footer a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ============ RESPONSIVE ============ */
    @media(max-width: 768px) {
      .stats-row { gap: 28px; }
      .cta-banner { padding: 40px 24px; margin: 20px 4% 60px; }
      footer { justify-content: center; text-align: center; }
      nav { padding: 16px 4%; }
      .nav-brand { font-size: 1.3rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="bg-orbs">
    <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-3"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav>
    <a href="/home" class="nav-brand">Zen<span>Track</span></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/auth" class="btn-login" id="nav-login-btn">Log In</a>
      <a href="/auth?signup=1" class="btn-signup" id="nav-signup-btn">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span class="dot"></span>
      🚀 Your habit tracking journey starts here
    </div>
    <h1>
      Build Habits.<br>
      <span class="gradient-text">Track Growth.</span><br>
      Live Better.
    </h1>
    <p>
      ZenTrack helps you build powerful daily habits with a beautiful visual tracker, analytics, and reminders — so you stay consistent every single day.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/auth?signup=1" class="cta-primary" id="hero-signup-btn">
        Start for Free <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
      </a>
      <a href="/auth" class="cta-secondary" id="hero-login-btn">
        <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Log In
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div class="stats-row">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">🔥 21</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Days to build a habit</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">100%</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Free to use</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">∞</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Goals you can track</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-num">📈</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Live analytics</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Why ZenTrack?</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Everything you need to stay consistent</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i></div>
        <h3>Daily Tracker</h3>
        <p>A beautiful monthly grid to check off your habits every day. One tap — one win. Watch your streak grow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
        <h3>Analytics & Insights</h3>
        <p>Visual charts showing your daily completion rate to keep you motivated and aware of your progress.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
        <h3>Goal Management</h3>
        <p>Add, edit or remove goals with ease. Build a personalized set of habits that matches your lifestyle.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-history"></i></div>
        <h3>Full History</h3>
        <p>Look back at previous months. Every day of your journey is recorded so you can track long-term growth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-bell"></i></div>
        <h3>Smart Reminders</h3>
        <p>Get notified at the right time to check off your daily goals. Never miss a day again.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
        <h3>Secure & Private</h3>
        <p>Your data is yours. ZenTrack is secure. Only you can see your progress and habits.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">How it works</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">3 simple steps to better habits</h2>
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <h3>Create your account</h3>
        <p>Sign up in seconds using email. No complicated setup, just fill the form and you're in.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <h3>Add your goals</h3>
        <p>Set your daily habits — exercise, reading, coding, meditation — anything you want to track.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <h3>Track every day</h3>
        <p>Check off your habits daily. Watch your consistency grow on beautiful charts and reports.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA BANNER -->
  <div class="cta-banner">
    <h2>Ready to level up your life? 🚀</h2>
    <p>Join ZenTrack today — completely free, no credit card required.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/auth?signup=1" class="cta-primary" id="cta-signup-btn">
        Create Free Account <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
      </a>
      <a href="/auth" class="cta-secondary" id="cta-login-btn">
        I have an account
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <div>© 2025 <strong>ZenTrack</strong> — Build better habits, one day at a time.</div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;">
      <a href="/auth">Login</a>
      <a href="/auth?signup=1">Sign Up</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
